reviewText: Would love to find the next one: putting it back together.
This video was detailed, high quality and well narrated. Suggestions and tips were also provided that were helpful.
Well detailed and clearly shown Ford Lehman Engine. With this I am confident I could rebuild a Ford Lehman myself!
A nice pace to see how an engine is tore down. Also a greatly organized work area makes sense.
It is very basic and easy to follow.. It' a must see if you are a boat owner..
